Company Overview of Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of May 6, 2016, Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund has gone out of business. Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund is an open-ended balanced mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Alternative Investment Advisers, Inc., Cliffwater Investments LLC, Brigade Capital Management, LLC, ICE Canyon LLC, Harvest Fund Advisors, LLC, LaSalle Investment Management (Securities) L.P., LLC, Lazard Asset Management LLC, and MAST Capital Management, LLC. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of countries across the globe. For its equity portion, the fund takes l...
As of May 6, 2016, Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund has gone out of business. Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund is an open-ended balanced mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Alternative Investment Advisers, Inc., Cliffwater Investments LLC, Brigade Capital Management, LLC, ICE Canyon LLC, Harvest Fund Advisors, LLC, LaSalle Investment Management (Securities) L.P., LLC, Lazard Asset Management LLC, and MAST Capital Management, LLC. It invests in public equity and fixed income markets of countries across the globe. For its equity portion, the fund takes long and short positions to invest in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. For its fixed income portion, the fund invests in fixed income securities including high-yield/high-risk fixed income securities, bank loans, distressed debt, corporate bonds, inflation-linked, and emerging market debt securities issued by diversified issuers which are of varying maturities and quality. It employs fundamental analysis along with a top down security picking approach to create its portfolio. The fund seeks to benchmark the performance of its portfolio against the HFRX Fixed Income Credit Index. It uses proprietary research to create its portfolio. Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Alternative Income Solution Fund was formed on April 23, 2014 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


100 Pearl Street9th FloorHartford, CT 06103United StatesFounded in 2014










