Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Strategic Income Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:31 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Strategic Income Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Strategic Income Fund is an open-ended fixed income mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Alternative Investment Advisers, Inc. and Newfleet Asset Management LLC. It invests in fixed income markets of countries across the globe. The fund invests directly and also uses derivatives like forwards, swaps, futures, and options to invest in fixed income securities issued or guaranteed by governments, their agencies, authorities or instrumentalities, and other issuers including collateralized mortgage obligations, real estate mortgage investment conduits, and other pass-through securities which are rated...
Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Strategic Income Fund is an open-ended fixed income mutual fund launched by Virtus Investment Partners, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Virtus Alternative Investment Advisers, Inc. and Newfleet Asset Management LLC. It invests in fixed income markets of countries across the globe. The fund invests directly and also uses derivatives like forwards, swaps, futures, and options to invest in fixed income securities issued or guaranteed by governments, their agencies, authorities or instrumentalities, and other issuers including collateralized mortgage obligations, real estate mortgage investment conduits, and other pass-through securities which are rated both investment and non-investment grade and can be of any maturity. It employs fundamental analysis along with a top-down security picking approach to create its portfolio. Virtus Alternative Solutions Trust - Virtus Strategic Income Fund was formed on September 8, 2014 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


100 Pearl Street9th FloorHartford, CT 06103United StatesFounded in 2014



www.virtus.com/our-products/mutual-fund/Strategic-Income/A







